reviewText: Being Jewish, this DVD really tickled my funnybone, especially some of the stuff Ron Reid said about being in that "later in life" age :-) which applies to me too. Highly recommend watching this one!
Had a great time!  Comedians were awesome!

I attended the show and had a great time. It is not very often that you get a bunch of Jewish comedians in the Pacific North West. Ranging several generations it was funny to see the different styles and interests, all connected to Jewish humor.
Enjoy (and go light on the guilt :-)...).
